txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Pure black skin from the worms surrounding Tyrn Lhuig. Delivery of the items should be made to Othran at the base of the hilltop outpost.
'The skin from worms can be used in several items and processes. If you have no need of it, we will gladly take it from you.'
Council of the North Task: Pure Black Skin
The hunters at Tyrn Lhuig expect a delivery of pure black skin to be made to Othran, one of their number at the bottom of their hillside outpost.
Deliver the pure black skin to Othran at Tyrn Lhuig in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver pure black skin from the worms surrounding Tyrn Lhuig to Othran at the bottom of the hillside outpost.
Wanted: Pure black skin from the worms surrounding Tyrn Lhuig.
